data.description: Huge Reduction by motivated Sellers! Plus $5,000 towards closing costs! Pool home in Holiday close to parks and the ocean. You will enjoy the fenced back yard oasis with a tiki bar, sun deck and a fire pit. Enjoy the day in the pool and then the evening around the fire pit. The home has new HVAC and ducts and water heater in 2020, renovation in 2018 included flooring, kitchen, pool and bathrooms, new induction stove and dishwasher 2022, and new pool pump and cleaner robot this year! Check out the cedar lined closets! This home has a lot of living space. There are so many pluses in the home you must see it for yourself!
